# Budget Buddy 💰📘

A minimalist budget tracking app for managing income and expenses without the stress.  
Built with React and TailwindCSS, this project is clean, responsive, and gives off strong *“I know how to code”* energy.

---

### 🔧 Features

- Responsive UI using TailwindCSS
- Placeholder layout with dark mode vibes
- Built with Vite + React
- Ready for expansion with actual budgeting logic someday (maybe)

---

